description:
Advertisement scheme consisting of (P2025/0084/LBC also submitted)
•1 no. circular projecting sign with Ceru Restaurant branding, and to be externally illuminated with trough illumination. Positioned ON left hand side of frontage (597 x 560mm);
•1 no. Menu Board sign positioned on right hand side of frontage beside restaurant entrance. Gold frame with white menu board that is back lit with white LED's (450mm x 600mm);
•1 no. 'Ceru Restaurants' entrance column lettering sign, positioned directly above menu board on right hand side of frontage. Former of flat cut brushed champagne stainless steel lettering (450mm x 193mm);
•4 no. fabric awning signs positioned above window glazing and featuring subtle Ceru Restaurants lettering (2510mm x 1100mm)
